TextBody:
Hello Cameron,
 
Thank you for your time today.
In today's meeting, I was unable to uninstall and reinstall AIC. While trying to uninstall the AIC, we get an error message "Windows is unable to stop the service for the Access Information Center"
I tried to disable the server, but that didn't work.
You rebooted the server that did not help.
 
I will review the log for more information. In the meantime, you can use the link below to schedule the follow-up meeting.
https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=sJxXIqzLWRZf8ZodxDdkQjtjoelAYi0D1ubHGDNoZMU-Z&MeetingID=uEv94apsg9Lz3w82OfCtRkdrfozWcgnAysq_taKlx3U-Z
 
Thanks,
